✅ Included Strategies

1. market_orders.py
Places real-time buy and sell market orders.

Example:

python
Copy
Edit
place_market_buy("BTCUSDT", 0.001)
2. limit_orders.py
Executes limit buy/sell at specified prices.

Example:

python
Copy
Edit
place_limit_buy("BTCUSDT", 0.001, 25000)
3. advanced/oco.py
Executes a One Cancels the Other (OCO) trade.

Automatically manages target + stop-loss together.

Example:

python
Copy
Edit
place_oco_order("BTCUSDT", 0.001, 28000, 24000, 23500)
4. advanced/twap.py
Runs Time-Weighted Average Price (TWAP) trades.

Breaks large order into multiple time-based chunks.

Example:

python
Copy
Edit
execute_twap("BTCUSDT", 0.01, 5, 10)
